    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but if it can't actually stop the big powers from doing whatever they want, isn't the \"legitimacy\" part just a way for them to make their actions look better? like, if a country ignores the UN to start a war, and the UN can't do anything about it, doesn't that basically prove the whole institution is just a tool for the status quo rather than a real way to maintain peace?",
