      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "That is a very astute observation, and it points directly to the core weakness of the liberal international order. When major powers disregard the UN, the institution functions less as a guarantor of peace and more as a public relations tool for the global community. This dynamic proves that the UN's power is entirely conditional upon the willingness of the strongest nations to abide by its mandates. Ultimately, the UN reflects the current balance of power, not a transcendent force for global peace.",
      "source": "target",
